        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="SeR68ESlQ_yLdG1FhVIL-4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#cdeb8b;strokeColor=#36393d;strokeWidth=2;align=left;" value="&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Verification Answer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;to q0:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;U.S. legal tender refers to coins and currency that are recognized by law as valid money for payments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Verification Answer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;to q1:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Because cash is legal tender in the United States, businesses are generally expected to accept it as payment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Verification Answer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;to q2:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;In some U.S. states, payment laws indicate that operating a completely cashless business is not legally permitted.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Verification Answer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;to q3:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Since U.S. currency is legal tender, merchants are not supposed to refuse it when offered for payment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;...&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
